synopsis: Come on a journey through time with this treasured collection of short stories for kids. From classic fables such as The Tortoise and the Hare (narrated by Morgan Freeman) to contemporary retellings of timeless folktales from around the world, such as the Tlingit legend Beyond the Mountains (narrated by Daisy Ridley), there’s sure to be something that any kid will love. Take a virtual trip to the past with this anthology of classic stories, including the Grimm Brothers' Hansel and Gretel (narrated by Meryl Streep) and the timeless tale of Ali Baba and the Forty Thieves (narrated by Will Smith). This collection will bring stories to life and spark imagination with its diverse cast of narrators. Enjoy the magical and captivating experience of these timeless stories and explore the many ways they can be used for educational and storytelling purposes. Young children and adults alike will be spellbound by this collection of short stories.
title: "Time Travellers: A Magical Anthology of Classic Stories"
